{"tid":400090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚睇我地雲加點樣淩辱對手la","createTime":"2017-09-14T13:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T01:38:08.000Z","uid":31314,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc6b28b28fb00207eda86ed29b6331b0ee5e2eb","tid":400090,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴今年雖然走了25張~但一支球隊吾會話走左一個人就會差成咁~<br />\n個人覺得藍斯攻擊力比25張更好~(不喜物插)~有待時間証明~<br />\n今屆無可否認開季比以往差左~但我寧願開季差D~之後慢慢追上來~<br />\n無記錯~都已勝了一仗~今屆好明顯雲加比過去更重視歐霸~<br />\n希望今晚可以殺低科隆~一鼓作氣過埋車路士呢關~<br />\n保持氣勢到季尾<br />\n各位巴打一條心支持阿仙奴今屆奪首個歐霸~~"},{"pid":"396014ff95d872ade4b8a5eb0f8f2c67f9dd429f","tid":400090,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8460f3bd54cab3120c0b4f1ae1d2122b0eca204","tid":400090,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"62e05a1f53ecd2b66bdc77c6fb7927da92506f5b","tid":400090,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"608dfe989919b26c36b013f6c500b4495afeb708","tid":400090,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/220102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F220102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dc04ee7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"795d12b7a11b9afd90fe454beba50c9f2d1b4d7b","tid":400090,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/220102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2